Overview: Dr. Enrique Diaz Guzman Zavala is a pulmonologist in Pensacola, Florida and is affiliated with University of Alabama at Birmingham Hospital. He received his medical degree from Tecnologico de Monterrey Escuela de Medicina and has been in practice between 11-20 years. He is one of 26 doctors at University of Alabama at Birmingham Hospital who specialize in Pulmonology. He also speaks multiple languages, including Spanish.
